description: The Tinker Board 3 is a compact, fanless single-board computer powered by the Rockchip RK3566 SoC, designed for embedded and IoT applications that require multi-display capabilities, wireless connectivity, or Gigabit Ethernet support. This board integrates a quad-core Arm Cortex-A55 processor with a 64-bit Arm v8 architecture. It comes with either 2GB or 4GB LPDDR4X memory […]
title: ASUS Tinker Board 3 SBC with Linux Support Starts at $89.59
